OL,6,FA man who arranged to meet and rape
OL,7,Ftwo children at a hotel has been
OL,8,Fjailed.
OL,10,FChristopher Hackett sent messages to
OL,11,Fwhat he thought was the mother of a 12-
OL,12,Fyear-old girl and an eight-year-old
OL,13,Fboy to organise a meeting at a hotel
OL,14,Fin Alfreton, Derbyshire.
OL,16,FHe sent explicit photos and described
OL,17,Fwhat he wanted to do.
OL,19,FHackett, of Town Lane, Rotherham, had
OL,20,Fin fact been communicating with an
OL,21,Fundercover police officer.
