OL,6,FWhen he arrived at the hotel, in
OL,7,FAlfreton, Derbyshire, he was arrested.
OL,9,FThe 37-year-old had items including
OL,10,Fsweets and fizzy drinks with him.
OL,12,FHis mobile phone was seized and found
OL,13,Fto contain thousands of explicit
OL,14,Fimages and videos of children.
OL,16,FHe was later charged with attempted
OL,17,Fsexual communication with a child,
OL,18,Farranging to commit a child sex
OL,19,Foffence and possession of indecent
OL,20,Fimages.
