OL,6,F"He spoke with a woman he thought was
OL,7,Fthe mother of two children and
OL,8,Farranged to meet her in order to rape
OL,9,Fthe children, and it is clear from the
OL,10,Fmessages he sent that he knew exactly
OL,11,Fwhat he was doing.
OL,13,F"Not only did he discuss his depraved
OL,14,Ffantasies but he also travelled to
OL,15,Fmeet this 'woman' to carry out his
OL,16,Fdespicable crime.
OL,18,F"I have no doubt that had he not been
OL,19,Fcaught, he would have gone on to cause
OL,20,Fsevere physical and psychological harm
OL,21,Fto children in the future."
